<section class="content">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
      <h4>Viewing Application for <%= @user.username %></h4>
      <p>Because you are a member of Central Command or Admissions you can view, accept and decline applications.
        When you accept an application, the user is automatically created on the forums with the correct groups.</p>
      <br></br>

      <p><b>Applying for game:</b> <%= @user.game_id %></p>
      <p><b>Date of Birth:</b> <%= @user.dob %></p>
      <p><b>Location:</b> <%= @user.location %></p>
      <p><b>Discord Username:</b> <%= @user.discord_username %></p>
      <p><b>Do you have and use a microphone?</b> <%= @user.mic %></p>
      <p><b>What game do you want to join us for, and why?</b> <%= @user.what_game_why %></p>
      <p><b>If applicable, are you joining us for Console gameplay? and if yes, which console?</b> <%= @user.console_gaming %></p>
      <p><b>Were you referred by a current member, if yes, who?</b> <%= @user.referring_member %></p>
      <p><b>Where did you hear about AceClan?</b> <%= @user.hear_ace %></p>
      <p><b>Would you have an interest in joining our Administrative Departments (e.g. Military Police or Admissions Team)?</b> <%= @user.admin_interest %></p>
      <p><b>Have you ever been in a clan like this before?</b> <%= @user.clan_before %></p>
      <p><b>Do you use a VPN to connect to the internet or play games?</b> <%= @user.vpn_connection %></p>
      <br></br>

      <% if @approval.denied == false && !@approval.approved_by %>
        <% prms = { approvals: { approved_by: current_user.id, approved_at: Time.now } } %>
        <%= link_to "Approve Application", approval_path(prms), method: 'patch', class: "btn btn-success", style: "float: left;" %>
        <% rprms = { approvals: { denied: true, denied_by: current_user.id, denied_at: Time.now } } %>
        <%= link_to "Deny Application", approval_path(rprms), method: 'patch', class: "btn btn-danger", style: "float: right;" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
